      <title>祖马因南非选举叛乱接受非洲人国民大会听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-18/zuma-faces-anc-hearing-over-his-south-african-election-rebellion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲人国民大会召开会议，决定是否取消前南非总统雅各布·祖马的党籍，因为他在今年的选举中为竞争对手竞选。彭博新闻社的 Khuleko Siwele 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-18/zuma-faces-anc-hearing-over-his-south-african-election-rebellion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:32:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
