    <item>
      <title>通胀开始缓解后，孟加拉国维持政策利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-holds-key-policy-rate-after-inflation-starts-to-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行维持关键政策利率不变，以支持经济增长并严格控制上个月刚刚开始缓解的通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-holds-key-policy-rate-after-inflation-starts-to-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
