      <title>OPEC+ 代表认为会议上不会改变油价上涨计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/opec-delegates-don-t-see-oil-hike-plan-changing-at-august-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+代表预计，该组织下个月的监督会议将是例行会议，不会改变从第四季度开始增加供应的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/opec-delegates-don-t-see-oil-hike-plan-changing-at-august-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:33:54 GMT</pubDate>
